4?t=1672425983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>While your party of unlikely heroes sets out to rescue a realm in distress, you’ll take cooking lessons with Mr. &amp; Mr. Giant, outsmart a gang of flies and prove yourself in the improvised game shows hosted by the guerilla unicorn Sylvester Stallione. Among other things. And, rumor has it, the fabled throne Up'Zhykling might be up for grabs as well. Give a green thumbs up and save Mirrormore!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287240/extras/48924072466193da1732cab52a0d104a.poster.avif?t=1672425983\" width=600 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287240/extras/48924072466193da1732cab52a0d104a.webm?t=1672425983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287240/extras/48924072466193da1732cab52a0d104a.mp4?t=1672425983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Siebenstreich’s Nerdventure...</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>...is a beautiful, hand-drawn indie adventure<br></li><li>...boasts lovingly hand-crafted dialogs<br></li><li>...presents a charming set of unconventional characters<br></li><li>...includes 14 songs composed exclusively for this game<br></li><li>...offers a seamlessly integrated help system<br></li><li>...is completely playable via gamepad<br></li><li>... also fully supports mouse controls, if you prefer the traditional point-and-click style<br></li><li>...contains only fair puzzles (according to our vegan carnivorous plant)<br></li><li>...ingeniously wraps the joy of a harmonious (*cough*) pen &amp; paper game night into a digital adventure<br></li><li>...is probably the first game to feature a truly adorable, vegan carnivorous plant</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop 